@WebApplication1_HostAddress = http://localhost:5129

### Health Check
GET {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Students
GET {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/students
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Student by ID
GET {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/students/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create New Student
POST {{WebApplication1_HostAddress}}/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "dateOfBirth": "2000-01-15"
}

